sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as SIDAT (Next.js)
    participant AI as AI Engine / Backend
    participant DB as Database (Supabase)
    actor Staf
    Admin->>Frontend: 1. Upload Surat (PDF)
    Frontend->>AI: 2. Kirim PDF untuk Ekstraksi
    activate AI
    AI-->>Frontend: 3. Kembalikan Ekstraksi JSON (Nama, Instruksi)
    deactivate AI
    Frontend-->>Admin: 4. Tampilkan "Review Form"
    Admin->>Frontend: 5. Validasi Data & Klik "Simpan & Distribusi"
    Frontend->>DB: 6. Simpan Data Surat & Target Staf
    activate DB
    DB-->>Staf: 7. Surat Muncul di Dashboard Staf
    deactivate DB
    Staf->>Frontend: 8. Lihat Detail & Baca Instruksi
    Staf->>Frontend: 9. Upload Dokumen Bukti Tindak Lanjut
    Frontend->>DB: 10. Update Status Disposisi ke "Completed"
    DB-->>Admin: 11. Status Berubah di Dashboard Admin
